      "side": 1,
      "message": "I am fine with (2) but I think it may be too restrictive. It will not allow library functions to access all defined variables. How about we provide three APIs?\n\nContextTestVar to access all variables defined in a test.\nContextFixtVar to access all variables defined in fixtures.\nContextBundleVar to access all variable defined in a bundle.\n\nIt is only for discussion. I have not had the code to do so.",
